   119→// PolicyRevisionBumpEvent queues an event for the given endpoint to set its
   120→// realized policy revision to rev. This may block depending on if events have
   121→// been queued up for the given endpoint. It blocks until the event has
   122→// succeeded, or if the event has been cancelled.
